# Sara's morning brief — install on her laptop or a small VPS.
#
# Install:
#   crontab -e
#   (paste the line below — adjust the repo path)
#
# Verify:
#   crontab -l
#
# 08:55 Mon–Fri (Europe/London). Monday's run naturally includes Sat+Sun
# because dedup state + source freshness windows go back 3 days.
#
# Set env vars in the wrapper rather than here (keeps secrets out of crontab).

55 8 * * 1-5  cd /ABSOLUTE/PATH/TO/VMA && ./run_brief.sh >> /tmp/vma-brief.log 2>&1
